             was indicted for <rs id="t17700530-58-off325" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17700530-58-off325" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17700530-58-off325" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing forty yards of callicoe, value 4 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17700530-58-victim548" type="victimName">
                     Charles
                      Napper
                  <interp inst="t17700530-58-victim548" type="surname" value="Napper"></interp>
