                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17700530-58-defend546 t17700530-58-punish333"></join>
               T
            </rs>. </p>
               <p>Wright <rs id="t17700530-58-verdict334" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17700530-58-verdict334" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
